      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Requirements for track headers:\n1 User can grab the whole timeline including track header and move it on y-axis when touches dragging area\n2 Change the all trackheader to another key (for example, change KeyT -> Super (win button))",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
